The paper discusses autonomous flight in GPS-denied and cluttered environments, which is a problem in robotics and control systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions the use of computer vision techniques for obstacle avoidance, which suggests cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the second likely sub-category. The paper also involves control systems and optimization, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), respectively. Finally, the paper mentions the use of machine learning techniques for perception and decision-making, which could also fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
